snippet.title: Welcome to Camp Summers Hill, Pinewood Valleys Prolouge Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Camp Summers Hill, the Prologue of Pinewood Valley   

Here is where you'll be starting the Story of Pinewood Valley.  

Set 20 years before in 1986

You play as Eli and play the role of a camp counselor with your friends, but this Night will change Eli forever.

Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/coldchopstudio/pinewood-valley-horror-game?ref=nav_search&result=project&term=Pinewood

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ColdChopStudios


#horrorgaming #horror #scarygaming #trailer #gametrailers #PinewoodValley
